<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Bishnoism</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>The Bishnoism</h1>
    <nav>
        <a href="#">Home</a>
        <a href="#">About</a>
        <a href="#">History</a>
        <a href="#">29 Rules</a>
        <a href="#">Books</a>
        <a href="#">Contact</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
    <h2>“A Living Tradition of Nature and Humanity”</h2>
    <p>Explore the history, sacrifice, and teachings of the Bishnoi community</p>
    <button>Explore Now</button>
</section>

<section class="about">
    <h2>About Bishnoi Community</h2>
    <p>
        The Bishnoi community, founded by Guru Jambheshwar Ji,
        follows 29 principles focused on environmental protection,
        compassion, and simple living.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="cards">
    <div class="card">
        <h3>🌳 History</h3>
        <p>Discover the legacy and sacrifice of 363 martyrs.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <h3>📜 29 Rules</h3>
        <p>Learn the core principles of Bishnoi life.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <h3>📚 Books</h3>
        <p>Read and buy books about Bishnoism.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 TheBishnoism.com | All Rights Reserved</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    background-color: #f5f5dc;
}

header {
    background: #2e7d32;
    color: white;
    padding: 15px;
    text-align: center;
}

nav a {
    margin: 10px;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
}

.hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 100px 20px;
    background: url('desert.jpg') no-repeat center/cover;
    color: white;
}

.hero button {
    padding: 10px 20px;
    background: #ffcc00;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.about {
    padding: 40px;
    text-align: center;
}

.cards {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 40px;
}

.card {
    background: white;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    width: 250px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

footer {
    background: #2e7d32;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 10px;
}
